item.title: Aircraft Model Collection in 2014
item.description: Some nonsenses… This post covers all my aircraft models which collected in 2014. Time flies very fasts…There was a large number models back to 2014. However, only 4 girls remained here today. ID Photo and Basic Information: Order from newest to oldest [Phoenix] China Airlines A330-300 B-18358 “Masalu Taiwan!” Special Colour Arrived at 2014-09-08. [JC Wings] All Nippon Airways B767-300, JA8674 “60 Years Anniversary” Special Colour Arrived at 2014-08-28.
